## ğŸ§  Database Design

### Entities
- **realms** â€“ distinct regions or domains
- **creatures** â€“ entities belonging to realms
- **abilities** â€“ skills or powers
- **creature_abilities** â€“ junction table (many-to-many)

### Relationships
- One realm â†’ many creatures
- Many creatures â†” many abilities

All relationships are enforced using foreign key constraints.

